        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Asking a conference. Important to decide something definite concerning Santa Anna</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>At <placeName><persName>Bell</persName>s</placeName> <date when="1836-07-02">Saturday July 2</date></p>

<p>Dr Sir,</p>

<p>I very much wish you would come to the house <date when="1836-07-02">tonight </date>or early 
<date when="1836-07-03">tomorrow morning</date>. It will not be much out of the way. I think it very 
important that something definite should be determined upon as to <persName>Santa Anna</persName>,
as soon as you reach the <persName>army </persName>yours respectfully</p>

<p><persName>S F Austin</persName></p>

<p><persName>Gen Lamar</persName></p>



        </div1>
    </body>
